{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">SFERA - Action platformer. A mix of 3D and retro 2D graphics.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/608380/extras/logo_rgb_hack.png?t=1736613849\" /> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">SFERA is an intergalactic association of assassins, operating under the cover of the robot union. You are an assassin for the SFERA corporation. You are tasked to carry out an order to eliminate out of control robots in the A7FA-3T system. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Destroy enemies, collect items and buy new weapons. Drone assistant, can attack enemies if upgraded. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/608380/extras/weapons_all.png?t=1736613849\" /> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Unusual planets and space base of A7FA-3T system with secret rooms. Enemies will make you show your wits and determination.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/608380/extras/space.png?t=1736613849\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The transition between planets is made on an intergalactic ship. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/608380/extras/space.gif?t=1736613849\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You need to fly through the stars smashing asteroids and collecting elements.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use headphones and gamepad for a more immersive experience. </p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/608380/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1736613849","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/608380/page.bg.jpg?t=1736613849","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/a